1 (7) Tier 7: One hundred thousand (100,000) square
2 feet of canopy and beyond, the fee shall be Fifty
3 Thousand Dollars ($50,000.00), plus an additional
4 twenty-five cents ($0.25) per square foot of
5 canopy over one hundred thousand (100,000) square
6 feet.
7 b. For an outdoor medical marijuana grow facility:
8 (1) Tier 1: Less than two and one-half (2 1/2)
9 acres, the fee shall be Two Thousand Five Hundred
10 Dollars ($2,500.00),
11 (2) Tier 2: More than two and one-half (2 1/2) acres
12 up to five (5) acres, the fee shall be Five
