ENGR. H. A. to ENGR. S. B. NO. 1242 Page 5

1 (6) Tier 6: More than thirty (30) acres up to forty
2 (40) acres, the fee shall be Forty Thousand
3 Dollars ($40,000.00),
4 (7) Tier 7: More than forty (40) acres up to fifty
5 (50) acres, the fee shall be Fifty Thousand
6 Dollars ($50,000.00), and
7 (8) Tier 8: If the amount of acreage exceeds fifty
8 (50) acres, the fee shall be Fifty Thousand
9 Dollars ($50,000.00) plus an additional Two
